quotes.1: “Impossible is for the unwilling” John Keats

quotes.3: “Each day I will accomplish one thing on my to do list.”

quotes.13: “One of the secrets of getting more done is to make a TO-DO List every day, keep it visible.”

quotes.14: “Don’t let yesterday take up too much of today.”

quotes.15: “Nothing is impossible. The word itself says “I’m possible!”

quotes.16: “Whatever you are, be a good one.”

quotes.22: “Dreaming, after all, is a form of planning.”

quotes.24: “I’m a slow walker, but I never walk back.”
